function Start()

	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idSelf, itemLetter, "QST_Frac_FaithInBlood")
	idPetrClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idPetr)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPetrClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPetrClone, idPetrWalkLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
		Hydra.QActorDeleteNPCClone(idPetrClone, 0.5)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idMotherClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idMother)
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convKveraIntro, idSelf, idMotherClone)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idMotherClone, 4)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idMotherClone, idMotherLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idMotherClone, idMotherLoc)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMotherClone) then
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idMotherClone, 0.5)
	end

end

	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idActorVictim, 1)

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idPetrClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idPetrHouse)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPetrClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPetrClone, idPetrRunLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idPetrClone, 0.5)
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOctaviaOutsideStart) then
		idOctaviaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idOctaviaOutsideStart, false)
		
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOctaviaClone) then
			Hydra.QActorWait(idOctaviaClone, 1)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idOctaviaClone, idOctaviaEndLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idOctaviaClone, idOctaviaEndLoc)
			Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idOctaviaClone)
		end
	end
	
end
